Y16 Hello World

Given a string as input represents the Name of the preson, Say Hello to them.

Input Format

Single String represents Name of the person.

Constraints

1<= String length <= 100.

Output Format

Hello String !!

Sample Input 0

Bob
Sample Output 0

Hello Bob !!
Sample Input 1

Alice
Sample Output 1

Hello Alice !!

Solution:

import java.io.*;
import java.util.*;

public class Solution {

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        String a;
        Scanner ik=new Scanner(System.in);
        a=ik.nextLine();
     System.out.println("Hello"+" "+ a +" !"+"!");
    }
}
